OL,3,CHow drones could be deployed to tackle
OL,4,CNI wildfires
OL,6,FThis year between January and July,
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland Fire and Rescue
OL,8,FService dealt with 1,370 wildfires.
OL,10,FA huge drain on resource.
OL,12,FOne of those was at Slieve Beagh - a
OL,13,Fbog that stretches 3,000 hectares
OL,14,Facross Tyrone, Fermanagh and Monaghan.
OL,16,FNow, a specialised drone is being
OL,17,Ftested to see if it could help protect
OL,18,Fthe peatland.
