OL,3,CHow drones could be deployed to tackle
OL,4,CNI wildfires
OL,6,FDrones would be used to monitor the
OL,7,Farea like CCTV and as a tool to tackle
OL,8,Fgorse fires.
OL,10,FRoy Spence is an environmental project
OL,11,Fofficer with The River Blackwater
OL,12,FCatchment Trust.
OL,14,FHe said: "The drone we are trying out
OL,15,Fis an agricultural drone and they are
OL,16,Fused all over the world for spraying
OL,17,Fweeds and spraying herbicides and
OL,18,Fthings.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
