OL,6,F"But we want it just to carry water.
OL,7,FThe one we have looked at carries 35
OL,8,Flitres.J"There's one that carries 100
OL,9,Flitres which is basically 100 kilos.
OL,11,F"That is the weight of a person and
OL,12,Fthat's a lot of water.
OL,14,F"So, if we can deploy that and get
OL,15,Fthat out there quickly, we can either
OL,16,Fsuppress the fire completely or we can
OL,17,Fcontain it until the fire service gets
OL,18,Fthere.
