OL,6,F"Some of the places on fire are really
OL,7,Fdangerous. There's big swallow holes
OL,8,Fand ravines and steep cliffs.
OL,10,F"It's not a good place to set fire
OL,11,Fcrews to. So, if we can access the
OL,12,Fharder parts with the drones and let
OL,13,Four fire crews stay on the easier
OL,14,Ftrack then that's another huge benefit
OL,15,Fof this, because obviously it doesn't
OL,16,Fmatter how rough the ground is for a
OL,17,Fdrone".
