OL,6,FSlieve Beagh is a special conservation
OL,7,Fsite but the wildfire back in May
OL,8,Fdestroyed much of the land and
OL,9,Fwildlife.J"The fire at Slieve Beagh
OL,10,Fwas probably the worst I've seen in 27
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,F"I've seen fires of that scale, but
OL,14,Fthe nature of the fire was horrendous.
OL,16,F"You look at the photographs of it,
OL,17,Fit's just black.
OL,19,F"It's like something from the
OL,20,Fapocalypse. It's horrendous.
