OL,3,CHow drones could be deployed to tackle
OL,4,CNI wildfires
OL,6,F"For days and weeks afterwards, we
OL,7,Fworked on surveillance, so we never
OL,8,Fsaw or heard a living thing up there,"
OL,9,FRoy said.
OL,11,FThe idea of using a drone to help
OL,12,Ffight wild fires is at a very early
OL,13,Fstage but would be a first for
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,16,FEach drone is around #30,000 - to Roy
OL,17,Fthat's cheap compared to the cost to
OL,18,Fthe environment.
