OL,6,FIn a statement, the Department of
OL,7,FAgriculture, Environment and Rural
OL,8,FAffairs said: "Ongoing financial
OL,9,Fcommitments have been made to help
OL,10,Frestore some of the areas previously
OL,11,Fimpacted by wildfires in Northern
OL,12,FIreland.
OL,14,F"New Peace Plus funding will support
OL,15,Ffurther wildfire initiatives at Slieve
OL,16,FBeagh.
