OL,3,CHow drones could be deployed to tackle
OL,4,CNI wildfires
OL,6,F"Additional spending has also been
OL,7,Fsecured to develop landscape scale
OL,8,Fwildfire management plans for three
OL,9,Fhigh-risk upland areas in Northern
OL,10,FIreland; the Mournes, Antrim Hills and
OL,11,FSperrins.
OL,13,F"The potential use of drones for
OL,14,Ftackling live wildfires would be a
OL,15,Fmatter for the Northern Ireland Fire
OL,16,Fand Rescue Service."
